No. 3383. Archer v Long,

April Term, 1894.

May 21, 1894,

On the call of this case for a hearing, an order was passed, on motion of D. E. Hydrick, Esq., attorney for respondent, dismissing the appeal under Rule 11 for failure ou the part of the appellant to file his points and authorities as required by Rule 8.
